high_descs: Walk forward, then turn right, and turn left when you reach the entertainment stand.
Pick up the newspaper from under the middle of the TV
Turn around and walk over to the white couch.
Place the newspaper to the right of the keys on the couch.
Turn around and walk back to the entertainment stand.
Pick up the newspaper to the right of the TV.
Walk back to the couch.
Place the newspaper to the left of the other one, on top of the keys.
anns.task_desc: Place two newspapers on a couch.

high_descs: Head towards the chair, then hang a right and face the TV set.
Pick up the newspaper from the back of the TV
Look around and walk towards the couch.
Put the newspaper to the couch.
Look around and head to the TV set.
Pick up the other newspaper from the side of the TV.
Walk towards the couch.
Put the newspaper to the couch.
anns.task_desc: Bring the two newspaper to the couch.

high_descs: Cross the room and turn right until you're standing in front of the console with the television on top.
Pick up the newspaper that's beneath the TV and closest to the right part of the TV stand.
Carry the newspaper to the sofa.
Place the newspaper on the rightmost cushion, which is the one closest to you.
Turn and move back to the console with the television.
Pick up the newspaper on the console to he right of the television.
Carry the newspaper back to the right end of the sofa.
Place the newspaper on the right cushion of the sofa to the left of the paper you previously put there.
anns.task_desc: Move two newspapers to the sofa.
